  "faq": {
    "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "q1": "Is FlacronCV really free?",
    "a1": "Yes! Our free plan lets you create 1 CV and 1 cover letter with basic templates. Upgrade to Pro for unlimited access.",
    "q2": "Can I export my CV as PDF?",
    "a2": "Absolutely! All plans support PDF export. Pro and Enterprise plans also support DOCX format.",
    "q3": "How does the AI writing work?",
    "a3": "Our AI analyzes your experience and the job description to generate tailored content. It uses advanced language models to create professional, impactful text.",
    "q4": "Is my data secure?",
    "a4": "Yes. We use enterprise-grade encryption, and your data is stored securely on Firebase. We are GDPR compliant and never share your information.",
    "q5": "Can I cancel my subscription anytime?",
    "a5": "Yes, you can cancel anytime. Your subscription will remain active until the end of your billing period.",
    "q6": "What languages are supported?",
    "a6": "FlacronCV supports English, Spanish, French, German, Arabic, and Urdu for both the interface and CV content."
